<item>
            <title>[LU-11468] LNet Health: Recovery interval</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11468</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Add a configurable parameter to determine the Recovery interval. It is likely that some sites might not want to do health pings on failed NIDs once per second. So allow the ability to configure the difference between each recovery ping.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
